BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 198.48000000000002 750 Td (THE 5-RECIPE ROTATION SYSTEM) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 100 740 m 512 740 l S Q
BT 0.2 g /F4 12 Tf 72 710 Td (The simplest meal planning system that actually works for ADHD brains:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 13 Tf 72 675 Td (THE CONCEPT:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 11 Tf 90 653 Td (Pick 5 dinners you can make on autopilot. Rotate them weekly.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 11 Tf 90 637 Td (Only add a new recipe when one of the 5 gets boring.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 13 Tf 72 607 Td (WHY IT WORKS:) Tj ET
